These, too, are for you.

243
00:20:25,300 --> 00:20:29,680
I got this style, especially for you. Aren't they cute?

244
00:20:32,060 --> 00:20:35,100
They're cute but just a little too pink.

245
00:20:35,100 --> 00:20:38,280
What's wrong with pink? Don't girls all like pink?

246
00:20:38,280 --> 00:20:39,800
Here.

247
00:20:51,500 --> 00:20:52,780
Are they new?

248
00:20:52,780 --> 00:20:54,440
Yeah.

249
00:20:55,840 --> 00:20:57,400
Over there.

250
00:21:06,100 --> 00:21:08,140
Did you buy all these?

251
00:21:09,660 --> 00:21:14,980
Your taste is even worse than my mom's.

252
00:21:14,980 --> 00:21:18,660
Why? Aren't they cute to you?

253
00:21:19,820 --> 00:21:22,040
Not as cute as you.

254
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:27,280
Spit it. What have you got up your sleeve?

255
00:21:28,140 --> 00:21:32,470
You're applying to be a research assistant. It's a lot, and time is tight.

256
00:21:32,470 --> 00:21:34,540
I can't give you special treatment.

257
00:21:34,540 --> 00:21:38,940
All I can do for you is provide private tutoring services.

258
00:21:38,940 --> 00:21:42,060
Look, this is all the material I've prepared for you.

259
00:21:42,060 --> 00:21:46,920
Although it's not super comprehensive, along with the papers I've helped summarize for you,

260
00:21:46,920 --> 00:21:50,400
getting the assistant job is pretty much guaranteed.

261
00:21:55,520 --> 00:21:57,440
You've prepared so thoroughly.

262
00:21:57,440 --> 00:22:00,860
Professor Gu, you've been planning this for a while.

263
00:22:02,580 --> 00:22:05,137
I just think your home is too far from school.

264
00:22:05,137 --> 00:22:09,444
With you commuting like this every day, won't it affect your study progress?

265
00:22:11,420 --> 00:22:17,680
Also, going home too late will disrupt Sister Lan's sleep, right?

266
00:22:17,680 --> 00:22:21,440
This is much better. Yunzheng Coffee Library,

267
00:22:21,440 --> 00:22:26,520
a private space just for you with personal service is open 24 hours for your use.

268
00:22:46,400 --> 00:22:50,280
That is your tip. Get me a cup of coffee.

269
00:22:50,840 --> 00:22:54,200
Your little tip is not enough for my coffee.

270
00:23:05,760 --> 00:23:07,640
That's more like it.

271
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:13,400
Wei'an, you're busy studying, and I'm busy with work.

272
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:18,180
If there's anything else, we might not even see each other once a week.

273
00:23:18,180 --> 00:23:20,420
We finally got together after so much difficulty.

274
00:23:20,420 --> 00:23:24,880
Starting today, I want to see you every day.

275
00:23:30,840 --> 00:23:32,180
Okay.

276
00:23:32,180 --> 00:23:34,400
Then I will...

277
00:23:35,160 --> 00:23:36,960
consider it.

278
00:23:40,520 --> 00:23:42,320
Consider it well.

279
00:23:54,120 --> 00:23:56,220
 Please open the door.

280
00:24:01,100 --> 00:24:02,660
What?

281
00:24:03,700 --> 00:24:06,940
Wei'an, did you move everything over?

282
00:24:06,940 --> 00:24:08,380
Yeah.

283
00:24:08,380 --> 00:24:09,860
Come here.

284
00:24:09,860 --> 00:24:11,760
What?

285
00:24:11,760 --> 00:24:14,860
Too much stuff? Or do you regret it now?

286
00:24:14,860 --> 00:24:18,740
I'll never regret it. Not too much stuff.

287
00:24:18,740 --> 00:24:24,400
I used to feel like my home was too empty, so it's good to fill it up a bit.

288
00:24:25,080 --> 00:24:30,060
So, are you not leaving tonight?

289
00:24:33,860 --> 00:24:36,740
The hospital is closer to your place, so it's more convenient for work.

290
00:24:36,740 --> 00:24:40,880
I can just go back home on the weekends from now on.

291
00:24:44,180 --> 00:24:49,640
Then how did you talk to Sister Lan about you moving in with me?

292
00:24:50,500 --> 00:24:55,700
I told her it was too busy in the lab, so the hospital arranged dorms for us.

293
00:24:57,640 --> 00:25:01,300
I just didn't mention that this dorm is super luxurious,

294
00:25:01,300 --> 00:25:05,540
and it also comes with 24-hour personal service.

